data.description: Adorable farmhouse and farm/homestead on over 1.3 acre lot. 3BR 2BA with eat-in kitchen and formal dining area. All bedrooms have walk-in closets. Freshly renovated with rustic laminate flooring and updated stainless appliances. Almost everything inside this home has been updated! Roof is 4 years old, water heater replaced 2 years ago, and HVAC unit replaced last year. Beautiful fenced backyard. 10x16 storage shed/barn included.
